7️⃣ payment_process.php
Purpose

🚨 CRITICAL TRANSACTION PAGE

Tables Used

bookings

payments

STEP 1: Prevent double booking
SELECT seat_numbers
FROM bookings
WHERE show_id = ?
  AND show_date = ?
  AND show_time = ?;


✔ Converts seat_numbers to array
✔ Checks overlap
✔ Stops booking if seat already taken

STEP 2: INSERT into payments
INSERT INTO payments
(email, show_id, seat_numbers, amount, payment_method,
 payment_status, transaction_id)
VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, 'Success', ?);


👉 Payment is stored first

STEP 3: INSERT into bookings
INSERT INTO bookings
(email, movie_id, theater_id, show_id, show_date, show_time,
 seat_numbers, total_price, status, payment_id)
VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, 'Confirmed', ?);


👉 Booking references payment_id

Why this order?

No payment → no booking

Maintains ACID consistency

8️⃣ success.php
Purpose

Show final ticket

Tables Used

bookings

movies

theaters

showtimes

payments

SQL Operation

✅ SELECT with JOIN

SELECT b.booking_id, m.name, m.poster,
       t.name, b.show_date, s.show_time,
       s.language, b.seat_numbers,
       b.total_price, p.payment_method,
       p.transaction_id
FROM bookings b
JOIN movies m ON b.movie_id = m.movie_id
JOIN theaters t ON b.theater_id = t.theater_id
JOIN showtimes s ON b.show_id = s.show_id
JOIN payments p ON b.payment_id = p.payment_id
WHERE b.booking_id = ?;

